title: Looking For Casual Ranked Team
body: Im curently in b5 and cant get out of it cause of the toxic nature of the game  just looking for a few ppl to play some ranked games with and go up in the elo. i play any lane but supp, i mainly play mid or adc. im in south australia play mostly late at night around midnight or during the day

replies.body: From the 15 games on your match history 2 of them you bought Mobis with homeguard  and just fed. I think you deserve bronze

Call a role, don't argue and type /mute all in chat as soon as you spawn.
Proceed to focus on ONLY what you can do to win the game

Congratulations, you're now not bronze
